</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 51.3021px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Docking station charger</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">20 €</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">£20</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">$20</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">$33</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 69.3056px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Adapter for plug (UK/US original charger)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">10 €</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">£10</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">$10</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">$17</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If an accessory is not listed in, and its value is less than 40 €/£/$ and no more than 10% of the item&#39;s price, the Agent may offer a commercial gesture based on the current market price, without needing to request the exact amount from the seller.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>For Trade-in</strong></span></h2>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>2.5.3 MAKING A COUNTEROFFER</strong><br>Counteroffers must be handled with care and tact, and you must provide as much information to the customer as possible so they fully understand why the amount is different from the original amount.<br>Back Market may pay the customer the initial price.<br><br>Back Market may use Credit Request tool charged at your expense in the following situations:</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 794px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 282.955px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Unjustified counter-offer</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">(displayed as “Refurbisher charter breach”)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 482.156px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You made a counter-offer that is clearly in violation of the rules listed in the Charter.<br>The customer shall be compensated so that they are paid the initial offer price.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 282.955px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Device false statement (displayed as “Refurbisher charter breach”)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 482.156px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You made a false statement about the device (e.g. wrong model not declared, wrong IMEI provided), which is at breach with quality charter. The customer shall be compensated so that they are paid the actual value of their device. </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 282.955px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Return fees</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 482.156px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You charged the customer for the shipping fees after a counter-offer refusal. The fees charged to the customer will be refunded. </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 282.955px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Missing accessories when device is sent back to customer</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 482.156px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You did not send the accessories back to the customer. The value of commercial gesture is determined thanks to the grid available in 3.6.2 section of Sales part of the Quality charter.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Where can I follow the Credit Requests I will be charged for? </span></h2>\n<p><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You can follow the Goodwill gestures at your expense in your Back Office.<br></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Where can I dispute commercial gestures?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you wish to dispute a credit request, please provide all the necessary information (at least the commercial gesture number) by submitting a request to the Seller Support Center.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Please ensure that your request is legitimate before sending it to the Seller Support Center. Otherwise, your request will not be processed by our teams.</span></p>"
